Large Hadron Collider (LHC) at CERN, Geneva, Switzerland
pinyin: Da4 xing2 Qiang2 zi3 Dui4 zhuang4 Ji1

sentences.english: The engineering of the electron-positron collider that we have completed also ranks among the world's most advanced technologies.
sentences.chinese: 我们的正负电子对撞机工程在全世界也是居于前列的。

sentences.english: Proving the existence of the Higgs boson is one of the main goals of the collider.
sentences.chinese: 而对撞机的工作就是要证实希格斯玻色子粒子的存在。

sentences.english: Help me out. Which ski cap says après-super-collider?
sentences.chinese: 帮我参考一下，哪顶滑雪帽比较像超级对撞机？

sentences.english: The Hubble Space Telescope has photographed many pairs of galaxies colliding.
sentences.chinese: 哈勃太空看远镜拍摄了很多对撞在一起的星系。

sentences.english: Character of impinging stream drying of bamboo high yield pulp was investigated.
sentences.chinese: 进行了半环对撞流干燥的流动与干燥特性实验。

sentences.english: Also, the impact angle has a great effect on the movement of the droplet impacting on the super- hydrophobic wall.
sentences.chinese: 撞击角度对撞壁后的液滴行为具有较大的影响。

sentences.english: Purchase all upgrades for the Meson Collider.
sentences.chinese: 购买所有升级介子对撞机。

sentences.english: By stealing vigor from incoming attacks, a mage guards himself against harm.
sentences.chinese: 通过从攻击中偷窃活力，法师守卫他自己对撞伤害。

sentences.english: The crushing of HMX was studied by impinge technology.
sentences.chinese: 利用对撞技术对HMX的粉碎进行了研究。
